node.text:
Hey everyone!!! I have some fun news to announce @XPPEN sent me their newest Artist Pro 16TP to review and they also want to team up with my to giveaway an Artist Pro 16!! 

For this contest all you have to do is redraw one of you’re past drawings, post it side by side with a short description of the character ! Like I did here in this post!!

Use the hashtag #xppen16th #redrawoldpainting and take me @missupacey, @xppen_ca and @xppenusa so we can see your entry! 

Be sure to get your entries in by the 24th of September!!! I’ll pick a winner then and @XPPEN will chose 2 other winners as well so that means you have 3 chances to win! 

Few rules: 
1. both traditional and digital art is acceptable
2. By participating you grant the rights to XP-Pen to share (with credit) the submission on social media
3. Multiple entries are welcome!
4. The winner will pay the custom duties themselves, if any, for the tablet 
5. Shipping is not available to Africa, the Middle East, South America, India and some island countries (contact @xppenusa for more info about that) 

And with that good luck everyone!!!
